OL,3,CReprimanded politician criticises
OL,4,Ccomplaints process as 'absurd'
OL,6,FA Guernsey politician has lambasted a
OL,7,Fcomplaint process that led to a formal
OL,8,Freprimand this week.
OL,10,FGuernsey's former Chief Minister Gavin
OL,11,FSt Pier was formally reprimanded by
OL,12,Fthe Bailiff for breaching the States
OL,13,FCode of Conduct on Wednesday 23
OL,14,FOctober.
OL,16,FDeputy St Pier was officially rebuked
OL,17,Ffor naming local paediatrician Sandie
OL,18,FBohin in a 2022 States speech as one
OL,19,Fof the clinicians involved in an
OL,20,Finvestigation into safeguarding
OL,21,Fconcerns.
