OL,3,CReprimanded politician criticises
OL,4,Ccomplaints process as 'absurd'
OL,6,FOn Wednesday's States sitting, some in
OL,7,Fthe house called for St Pier to
OL,8,Fapologise.
OL,10,FHowever, on Thursday 24 October,
OL,11,FDeputy St Pier released a statement
OL,12,Fwhere he described the time taken to
OL,13,Fprocess the complaint as "absurd",
OL,14,Fadding that the code of conduct
OL,15,Fprocess should never have been used in
OL,16,Fthis way.
