OL,3,CReprimanded politician criticises
OL,4,Ccomplaints process as 'absurd'
OL,6,F"We all know there is an inherent
OL,7,Fimbalance in the relationship between
OL,8,Fpatients and their medical
OL,9,Fpractitioners which prevents many
OL,10,Fpeople from speaking out.
OL,12,F"I have been elected to represent the
OL,13,Fcommunity and that includes giving a
OL,14,Fvoice to the voiceless, which I will
OL,15,Fcontinue to do so long as I serve in
OL,16,Fthis role.
